m-usecases__card'><img src='https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0704/2642/7614/files/6db0ebe78548cf89d011eb0dfb4db96f.png?v=1780990815' alt='アパレルのShop the lookイメージ' loading='lazy'><h3>アパレル</h3><p>Shop the lookで着用イメージから商品詳細へ。</p></article><article class='cream-usecases__card'><img src='https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0704/2642/7614/files/72fd8986095864800070d4a14b620617.png?v=1780990814' alt='コスメ・美容のBefore and afterイメージ' loading='lazy'><h3>コスメ・美容</h3><p>Before & afterで変化や使用感をわかりやすく。</p></article><article class='cream-usecases__card'><img src='https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0704/2642/7614/files/d314886a4225b31a081ec01c358051b8.png?v=1780990815' alt='食品・D2Cの販促イメージ' loading='lazy'><h3>食品・D2C</h3><p>ストーリー、レビュー、定期的な販促をまとめて表現。</p></article><article class='cream-usecases__card'><img src='https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0704/2642/7614/files/3be2d760feaa5d936460a7d2e8807596.png?v=1780990815' alt='実店舗併設のMap導線イメージ' loading='lazy'><h3>実店舗併設</h3><p>Mapや告知導線で来店とECをつなげる。</p></article></div></div></section>",
